  "text": "Digital image forgery methods can be classified two main categories. One of them active methods and the other passive(blind) methods [CITATION_1] . Active methods must be have preembedded information, such as digital watermarking and steganography. Digital watermarking is a method embedding secret information in the data, can be divided two categories, visible and invisible [CITATION_2] . Steganography's example of digital signatures.",
